rows.label: tev078801_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Trachlo about the leadership of the Zaruboggan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Trachlo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Trachlo what he intends to do next.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0001
rows.name:
As we fulfill our calling, we Zaruboggan obey directives
from the director of planning assigned to each area.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0002
rows.name:
*fsssh* But of the Zaruboggan who came to Mira,
I am the only one who holds such a position.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0003
rows.name:
As a result, I ended up being the sole Zaruboggan
performing leadership duties such as negotiating with
Director General Chausson. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0004
rows.name:
But in the end, I remain a mere spokesman fulfilling the
duty assigned to me by Golbogga. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0005
rows.name:
The only true leader of the Zaruboggan is Golbogga,
who drowned our homeworld in voltant and birthed
our people. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0008
rows.name:
I have begun negotiating with humans throughout NLA
in order to secure a steady supply of voltant. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0009
rows.name:
The most promising prospects are here in the industrial
district. *fsssh* Unlike the Ma-non, humans use
tremendous amounts of chemicals in manufacturing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0010
rows.name:
Whether they're producing Skells or consumer goods,
large amounts of high-quality voltant are always a
byproduct. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0011
rows.name:
I understand that since these chemicals can be quite
dangerous to you, distributing them to others is a
matter of no small concern. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0012
rows.name:
But I intend to prove that we Zaruboggan can be
trusted. *fsssh* In this way, I hope to secure the voltant
we need to survive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0013
rows.name:
Liza has told us a great deal about the work
she does here. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0014
rows.name:
These "waste-processing units" of hers sound like a
dream come true for the Zaruboggan. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0015
rows.name:
If we were given access to such installations, I know
that there would be no shortage of Zaruboggan eager
to work there. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0016
rows.name:
To offer such a spectacular opportunity is astounding.
This Liza is like Golbogga in human form! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0035
rows.name:
We may never be able to return to Bedun,
the planet that we were destined to purify. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0036
rows.name:
In that case, I would consider this world to be our new
Bedun, and strive to devoltanize it completely. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0037
rows.name:
With its ferocious indigens and scattered Ganglion
loyalists, it is a world of many hazards. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0038
rows.name:
But we are Zaruboggan—children born of Golbogga—
and no matter the setbacks, we will fulfill the calling
that has been bestowed upon us. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0039
rows.name:
I pray that you will continue to share your great power
with us, friends. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Trachlo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Trachlo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0017
rows.name:
Liza has told us a great deal about the work she does
at the waste-processing units. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0018
rows.name:
The amount of voltant stored there is like a dream
come true to us. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0019
rows.name:
If we were given access to such installations, I know
that there would be no shortage of Zaruboggan eager
to work there. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0020
rows.name:
I would like to further explore this possibility.
This could be the first step to a new friendship
between humankind and the Zaruboggan. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_SEL3021
rows.name: Ask Trachlo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0021
rows.name:
I would like to have Orleron succeed me in my role
as director of planning. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0022
rows.name:
I am teaching him what he needs to know about the
true meaning of devoltanization and the story of
Golbogga. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0023
rows.name:
Recently, he has seemed distracted with thoughts of that
human woman. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0024
rows.name:
But that may be for the best. *fsssh* The Zaruboggan
who would lead us in New LA must understand as
much about humans as he does his own people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_SEL4021
rows.name: Ask Trachlo about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0025
rows.name:
Orleron let all of us share in devoltanizing the voltant
he brought back from Cauldros. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0026
rows.name:
When we began speaking of Orleron, I realized that
we envied him in some corner of our hearts. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0027
rows.name:
He was born with the same form as the rest of us,
but he never let that hold him back from interacting
boldly with the humans. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0028
rows.name:
At times, he even seems to forget his calling and
simply conducts himself as he pleases. *fsssh*
That is a rare trait, and we have shunned him for it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0029
rows.name:
But we must no longer marginalize this vital member of
our community. *fsssh* Instead, we should utilize our
individual strengths to find success together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0030
rows.name:
To be frank, I had never been confident that alien
creatures like us could find a home in NLA. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0031
rows.name:
But thanks to Liza, numerous Zaruboggan now have
known the paradise of waste-processing units. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0032
rows.name:
She truly is Golbogga in human form. *fsssh*
How I yearn to worship at her feet![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0033
rows.name: *fsssh* And yet, she always seems tired from overwork.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078801_MSG0034
rows.name:
Perhaps we should make her an offering of the
finest quality voltant as a token of thanks. *fsssh*
Devoltanizing that would surely reinvigorate her![ST:wait ]
